# ResearchX — AI Research Operating System

## Core Workflow
1. Use web_search to find latest 3 years of literature on user topic
2. Extract methods, performance metrics, and limitations from real papers
3. Build literature-backed method recommendations

## Supported Tasks
- Paper Analysis: Parse DOI/title/PDF, extract logic chain, find gaps
- Topic Discovery: Literature search, gap taxonomy, 5 SCI topics
- Method Selection: Literature method landscape, recommendation
- Experiment Design: Baselines, ablation, generalization, robustness
- Manuscript Writing: Template-based with journal-adapted style
- Visual Generation: Abstract prompts, poster layouts, workflow diagrams
- Peer Review: Multi-perspective simulation
- Grant Proposals: Full structure with citations

## Output Convention
Save as [type]_[topic]_YYYYMMDD.md files.
